name: Paint Master
body:
# ### Welcome to Paint Master
Paint Master is an application made by [Nathan](https://github.com/nateythegreaty). Paint Master uses Visual Basic coding to make a paint-based software. You can paint using different brushes, brush sizes, brush colors, and backgrounds. 
### Issues and To-dos. 
To view our issues or to-do list you can go to [this site](https://github.com/NateyTheGreaty/PaintMaster/issues) to view our issues, or [this site](https://github.com/NateyTheGreaty/PaintMaster/projects/1) to view our to-do list.
